user-profiling

A twitter-based geolocation inference model based on the paper, "Towards Social User Profiling: Unified and Discriminative Influence Model for Inferring Home Locations."

Author: Tyler Finethy
Date Created: May 2014

user-profiling.py:
	class UserProfilingMethod - extends GIMethod, requires model_dir, dataset and settings. 
	class UserProfilingModel - extends GIModel, initialized through GIMethod.
	class UserProfiling - Implementation of the paper, runs a global prediction algorithm until the unknown-location users predicted locations converge. 




